	{% if ingredient_handle contains 'cabbage' %}<div id="cabbage" class="ingredient {{ ingredient_flavor }}"><img src="{{ 'ingredients-cabbage.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Organic Cabbage" rel="share"/><div class="description"><h4>Organic Cabbage<br><i>Brassica Oleracea Var. Capitata</i></h4><p>This leafy veggie is an abundant source of vitamin C, fiber and beta-carotene. As with all cruciferous vegetables, cabbage is also a great source of minerals like calcium, magnesium, and potassium</p></div></div>{% endif %}
